name: Pac-Man Collection
description: From 2D to 3D, Pac-Man has been through it all.Now, you can relive four of his greatest adventures in Pac-Man Collection, which includes the original Pac-Man, the fast Pac-Attack, and the challenging Pac-Mania.A special Pac-Man Arrangement mode offers more power-ups and items for you--and the ghosts--to use.Over the years, the pellet-mucher has learned how to dodge, eat, and jump over ghosts, but the chase continues.
